---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms and Conditions | Dove Cottage"
  description="Read the website terms and conditions for using the Dove Cottage Day Hospice website."
>
  <section class="terms-page">
    <div class="container terms-container">
      <p class="terms-eyebrow">Legal Information</p>
      <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="terms-updated"><strong>Last updated:</strong> 27 April 2026</p>

      <p>
        These terms and conditions govern your use of the Dove Cottage Day Hospice website. By using this site,
        you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the website.
      </p>

      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Dove Cottage Day Hospice is a registered charity providing palliative care and family support. For website
        enquiries, please contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@dovecottage.org">admin@dovecottage.org</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Use of This Website</h2>
      <p>You agree to use this website lawfully and responsibly. You must not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the site in any way that breaches applicable laws or regulations.</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to systems, data, or services.</li>
        <li>Introduce malicious software, harmful code, or disruptive material.</li>
        <li>Use content in a way that could damage the charity's reputation.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Content and Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to keep website content accurate and up to date. However, information is provided for general
        guidance and may be updated or changed at any time without notice.
      </p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        Unless stated otherwise, all website content, design, text, graphics, and branding are owned by or licensed
        to Dove Cottage Day Hospice. You may view or print content for personal, non-commercial use only.
      </p>

      <h2>Donations and Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Some services (including forms, payment providers, maps, and embedded tools) may be delivered through
        third-party platforms. Their own terms and privacy policies also apply when you use those services.
      </p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to external websites for convenience and further information. We are not
        responsible for the content, availability, or policies of third-party websites.
      </p>

      <h2>Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Dove Cottage Day Hospice is not liable for any indirect or
        consequential loss arising from use of this website. Nothing in these terms excludes liability that cannot be
        limited by law.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. The latest version will always be published on this page with
        the updated date.
      </p>

      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes relating to website use are subject
        to the jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .terms-page {
    background: #f5f7fc;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0;
  }

  .terms-container {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .terms-eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: var(--type-micro);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-steel-blue-1);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: #0f2240;
  }

  .terms-updated {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: #435b7c;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem;
    color: #15305b;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
  }

  p,
  li {
    color: #2c3f5d;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 1.2rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-steel-blue);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
